Hello Jeyachandran! Thank you for coming in today. I'm Jeyachandran, the hiring manager, and I'll be conducting your technical round of the interview. Let's get started!

From your resume, I noticed that you've had several internship experiences in various roles, including AI project developer, data engineer, and web and app developer. Can you tell me about your experience in AI project development, specifically the web app you developed for mock interviews using AI to ask voice-based questions?
